# Aucctus Theme System Reference

Complete reference for Aucctus theme classes. Use these as your primary styling method.

---

## Core Principle

**ALWAYS use Aucctus theme classes first**, then supplement with Tailwind utilities only when necessary.

---

## The `cn` Utility

```typescript
import { cn } from '@libs/utils/react';

// Object notation for conditional classes
const className = cn(
  'base-class',
  {
    'conditional-class': condition,
    'another-class': anotherCondition,
  },
  propsClassName,
);
```

